					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(213153); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=213153&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227389" alt="DrClef" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=213153)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(213153); return false;" >DrClef</a></span> <span class="odate time_1321647585 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">18 Nov 2011 20:19</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1309322">
									

<p>Okay. I am going to say this once and only once, so listen well.</p>
<p>I am fucking sick and tired of this stupid fucking sharks and bees thing. This was funny once, twice, even three times. It got old around the hundredth. It has now passed beyond old into ancient. This joke is so fucking old that archaeologists dig for it through the strata of unfunny and nonhumorous, wrap it in plastic, and then take it to joke museums for people to marvel at and wonder how people ever even found this funny. The joke is so fucking lame that it makes Joe Theismann's leg after being sacked by Lawrence Taylor look like a stubbed toe.</p>
<p>So to the next fucking person to try another &quot;lol sharks, lol bees,&quot; joke, I say to you, &quot;YOU ARE NOT FUNNY OR CLEVER, PLEASE KILL YOURSELF.&quot;</p>
<p>That is all.</p>

